data.description: Gates Four/Golf Community-Jack Britt Schools!! Super amazing brick home, side entry garage on large estate lot.  Oversized back yard has a privacy fence and large deck for entertaining. Two large matching family rooms with fireplaces upstairs, and downstairs. The upstairs family room has built in wet bar.  Formal dining room, eat in kitchen. 5 Bedrooms, 4.5 Baths, Huge Finished Bonus Room, Master suite downstairs, 2 other bedrooms downstairs, two bedrooms upstairs, Eat in Kitchen w/Granite Countertops, Deck overlooking Privacy Fenced Back Yard! This is a large home for an entertaining family. Tons of open storage in the upstairs attic.
